plot: The Hawaii trip concludes with the ladies questioning Vicki about the status of her relationship with Brooks, and one last attempt by the ladies to get "Fancy Pants" Dubrow to put on her party pants. Back on the mainland, Heather introduces the ladies to her future neighbor, Shannon Beador, and Tamra invites the women over for a spooky-themed night of food and tarot card readings. At a dinner, Tamra reveals that she misses her kids and is thinking about having a baby with Eddie. After meeting the ladies, Shannon invites them over to her house for a "real" home cooked meal.—Anonymous
